		<h1 class="pageTitle">Exciting Careers</h1>
		
	</div>

	<div class="pageContent row">
		<div class="col-sm-9 editor">
			
			
			<p dir="ltr"><span><span><img class="largeimage img-responsive" src="../img/uploads/apply_now.png" alt="" /></span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span id="docs-internal-guid-19f4edb0-0ee2-9f42-3342-53dc6a3c4116"><span>Looking to build a career in the exciting and dynamic technology field at a company that values people? When you join the Repeat team you&rsquo;ll get to experience the latest technologies while enjoying life in upstate New York. Best of all, you get to be a part of a team that is passionate about client service. It&rsquo;s no wonder the Times Union voted Repeat Business as one of the </span><a href="http://www.topworkplaces.com/frontend.php/regional-list/company/timesunion/repeat-business-systems"><span>Top Places to Work</span></a><span> for three years running!</span></span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr"><span>Work With the Latest Technologies</span></h2>
<p dir="ltr"><span>As a partner with global technology leaders our team gets to experience leading technologies. From advanced network solutions to workflow and document management systems, we are closely aligned with global technology partners like Microsoft and Ricoh. This means you&rsquo;ll get world-class training as you work with the latest innovations.</span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr">Enjoy Life In Upstate New York</h2>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Forget travel and relocating. You can build a technology career right here in upstate New York. We love our state and local communities. We live, work, and volunteer in our communities. </span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr"><span>Serve Local Organizations</span></h2>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Repeat serves the office technology needs of a wide variety of business, nonprofit, and public-sector organizations. Whether your passion is sales, service, or administration, you&rsquo;ll enjoy getting to know hundreds of local leaders as we serve a wide variety of leading companies. </span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr"><span>Career Opportunities</span></h2>
<p dir="ltr"><span>As a growing company, we have a wide variety of opportunities open at any given time. </span></p>
<h3 dir="ltr"><span>Sales </span></h3>
<p dir="ltr"><span>The best place to build a sales career is a company that cares about its clients. Our sales team benefits from the competitive advantage provided by our responsive support and sterling local reputation. </span></p>
<h3 dir="ltr"><span>Technical Support</span></h3>
<p dir="ltr"><span>If you have a passion for technology and serving people you&rsquo;ll discover a variety of technical support positions including network support and copier/printer repair. You&rsquo;ll get access to the latest support technologies and consistent training to equip you to work efficiently and effectively.</span></p>
<h3 dir="ltr"><span>Administration</span></h3>
<p dir="ltr"><span>Our administrative support team works together to ensure client satisfaction. From dispatching service technicians to managing billing, you&rsquo;ll get to be a part of a team that cares about its clients and each other.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: bold;">Apply Now</span></h2>
<p>To apply please email a copy of your resume to <a href="mailto:info@repeatbusinessalbany.com">info@repeatbusinessalbany.com</a>.</p>
<hr style="width: 100%;" width="100%" /> 
			
